* [cite_start]**Practice Set 15.2**: 1. 180 sq cm 2. 117.15 sq cm 3. 336 sq cm 4. 68 cm [cite: 1931]
* [cite_start]**Practice Set 15.3**: 1. 88 sq cm 2. 42 cm 3. 40 sq cm [cite: 1931]
* [cite_start]**Practice Set 15.4**: 1. 756 sq cm 2. 690 sq cm 3. 570 sq cm [cite: 1931]
* [cite_start]**Practice Set 15.5**: 1. 6000 sq m 2. 776 sq m [cite: 1931]
* [cite_start]**Practice Set 15.6**: 1. (1) 2464 sq cm, (2) 346.5 sq cm, (3) 962.5 sq cm 2. (1) $2\sqrt{56}$ cm, (2) 22.4 cm, (3) 126 cm 3. 500.50 sq m 4. 616 sq cm [cite: 1931]
